<div class="container inf_admin">
  <div class="row inf_admin_header no-margin_mb">
    <div class="col-md-12 mb_line_break_reverse no-gap">
      <h3 class="basic_header">상품 판매 신청</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-12 no-gap_mb">
      <div class="col-md-6 prdt_apply_process no-gap_mb">
        <div class="col-xs-4 text-center prdt_apply_process_3cols">
          <i class="fa fa-lg fa-arrow-right"></i>
          <div class="circle_default">
            <span>1</span>
          </div>
          <p class="prdt_apply_process_desc">신청<br class="mb_line_break">상품 조회</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-4 text-center prdt_apply_process_3cols">
          <i class="fa fa-lg fa-arrow-right"></i>
          <div class="circle_selected">
            <span>2</span>
          </div>
          <p class="prdt_apply_process_desc">샘플<br class="mb_line_break">수령 정보 입력</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-4 text-center prdt_apply_process_3cols">
          <div class="circle_default">
            <span>3</span>
          </div>
          <p class="prdt_apply_process_desc">사용 정보<br class="mb_line_break">입력</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div><!-- .row -->

  <div class="row" style="padding-bottom:100px;">
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <h3 class="sample_complete_header">샘플 수령 신청이 접수되었습니다.</h3>
      <div class="col-md-12">
        <p class="sample_complete_middle">
          브랜드 : <%= @influencer_stores_product.product.brand %><br>
제품명 :  <%= @influencer_stores_product.product.name %><br>
제품 번호 : <%= @influencer_stores_product.product.id %><br>
옵션 : <%= @influencer_stores_product.option %><br>
수령인 : <%= @influencer_stores_product.destination.receiver %><br>
연락처 : <%= @influencer_stores_product.destination.phone_number ? @influencer_stores_product.destination.phone_number : @influencer_stores_product.destination.tel %><br>
        </p>
      </div>
      <h5 class="sample_complete_bottom"> 신청하신 내용이 승인되면 상품 배송이 진행됩니다.<br>
상품을 받으시면 3일 이내에 사용 정보를 입력해 주시기 바랍니다.</h5>
      <div class="col-md-12">
        <%= link_to "신청내역조회", cms_influencer_stores_products_path, class: "btn session_btn_black" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
